  "text": "Under stress conditions, eNOS translocates from the sarcolemma to the mitochondria [CITATION_1] with an essential role of lipid rafts [CITATION_2] or signalosomes [CITATION_3] . There is still an ongoing debate on whether mitochondria also contain functional NOS (for review see: [CITATION_4] ) and contribute to overall NOÁ generation in cardiomyocytes [CITATION_5] .",
